{"tid":949961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱落去七仔交電話費 見到個小朋友比警察罰企","createTime":"2018-12-21T07:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T08:57:00.000Z","uid":222659,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"49fadf43078ac6884eed40ed0553df1b03d656b5","tid":949961,"uid":222659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n見到有一個便裝同一個著住制服嘅差佬的咗小朋友企係7仔門口 又聽到打比佢老母<br />\n個小朋友多汗漬 個look似啱啱踢完波<br />\n見到佢想喊 好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係你 你會唔會主動問咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBy the way 上次都係同一間7仔 見到有個制服中佬叫人幫佢買煙 買完之後一手交錢比返條友 一手拎盒煙放係褲袋<br />\n買盒煙都等唔到收工買 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無見過類似事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3510de3664d899b06e5e49889614c27654fd5c00","tid":949961,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"係咪盪失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270e708009ca9f52790e65d0cbae5ad8c1aa5fed","tid":949961,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fdc7d4b70a1764611fc59ece824fdea8776e131","tid":949961,"uid":149013,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"可能搵吾到佢啊媽掛"},{"pid":"4de2ba1456db104790f28d129ae43324bcec8772","tid":949961,"uid":222659,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"3510de3664d899b06e5e49889614c27654fd5c00","tid":949961,"uid":136186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"係咪盪失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"應該唔會<br />\n我住哥頭唔會盪失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cb921410423c65341c7edb0907b4cca1b9df52",